    "description": "面向个人、MSP 和 IT 专业人员的远程连接管理软件。",
    "homepage": "https://devolutions.net/remote-desktop-manager/",
    "license": "Proprietary",
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://cdn.devolutions.net/download/Setup.RemoteDesktopManager.2025.3.29.0.msi"
        },
        "arm64": {
            "url": "https://cdn.devolutions.net/download/Setup.RemoteDesktopManager.2025.3.29.0.msi"
        }
    },
    "pre_install": [
        "if (!(is_admin)) { error \"$app requires admin rights to install\"; break }"
    ],
    "installer": {
        "script": [
            "Start-Process -Wait msiexec \"/i `\"$dir\\Setup.RemoteDesktopManager.$version.msi`\" /qn /norestart INSTALLDIR=\\\"$dir\\\"\""
        ]
    },
    "uninstaller": {
        "script": [
            "if (!(is_admin)) { error \"$app requires admin rights to uninstall\"; break }",
            "$msi = Get-ChildItem \"$dir\\Setup.RemoteDesktopManager.*.msi\" | Select-Object -First 1",
            "if ($msi) {",
            "    Start-Process -Wait msiexec \"/x `\"$($msi.FullName)`\" /qn /norestart\"",
            "}"
        ]
    },
    "notes": [
        "Remote Desktop Manager 已安装！",
        "",
        "特性：",
        "  - 统一的远程连接管理",
        "  - 凭据管理和安全存储",
        "  - 支持多种连接协议（RDP, SSH, VNC, 等）",
        "  - 团队协作和共享功能",
        "",
        "版本：2025.3.29.0",
        "",
        "注意：",
        "  - 安装需要管理员权限",
        "  - 首次安装时会自动计算 hash 并验证",
        "  - 如果下载失败，请手动访问官网下载",
        "",
        "官网：https://devolutions.net/remote-desktop-manager/",
        "文档：https://docs.devolutions.net/RDM/",
        "论坛：https://forum.devolutions.net/",
        "",
        "更新：scoop update RemoteDesktopManager",
        "卸载：scoop uninstall RemoteDesktopManager"
    ],
    "checkver": {
        "url": "https://devolutions.net/remote-desktop-manager/download/",
        "regex": "Version: ([\\d.]+)"
    },
    "autoupdate": {
        "architecture": {
            "64bit": {
                "url": "https://cdn.devolutions.net/download/Setup.RemoteDesktopManager.$version.msi",
                "hash": {
                    "mode": "download"
                }
            },
